Review_Url:
Story-line => 3/5 (Pretty linear and straightforward);
Acting => 4/5 (Synced with characters);
Directing => 5/5 (The presentation was so nice that even an adult like me who is into complex plots enjoyed it);
Visual Effects/Animation => 4/5 (Soothing);
Screenplay => 4/5 (Full of positivity);
Personal Recommendation => 5/5 (I enjoyed the whole movie. You can watch it alone or with anyone of any age and all of you will enjoy it. The wholesomeness in the movie release stress to a deep level.);
